'''Alokolum''' is a town in [[Gulu District]] in the [[Northern Region, Uganda|Northern Region]] of [[Uganda]]. It is home to a seminary, Alokolum Major Seminary.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://catholicleader.com.au/news/full-seminaries-under-threat_76192|title=Full seminaries under threat|work=The Catholic Leader|date=11 September 2011|publisher=}}</ref>

